thread.title: Jesse Lloyd
thread.title_full: National Storage reviewed by Jesse Lloyd

author: Jesse Lloyd
title: Jesse Lloyd
text:
I stored some goods from a deceased estate at national storage Mornington, the staff were helpful and professional, I live overseas and had to use removalists and communicate via email, it was all very smooth no glitches at all,
No bs charges, would definitely use them again.
